REGEDIT

* This file is used to register Microsoft Word Viewer 6.0.  It is required
* to be either in the Windows directory or the WORDVIEW.EXE directory.
* It should be in the WORDVIEW.EXE directory if Word is to be run off the
* network.

HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\.DOC = Word.Document.6
HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\.DOT = Word.Document.6

ENTRIES FOR Document SERVER

HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\Word.Document.6 = Microsoft Word 6.0 Document
HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\Word.Document.6\shell\open\command = wordview.exe %1

